{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"URL","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL_API\">URL API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>URL</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/URL\"><code>URL()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/hash\"><code>hash</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/host\"><code>host</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/hostname\"><code>hostname</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/href\"><code>href</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/origin\"><code>origin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/password\"><code>password</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/pathname\"><code>pathname</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/port\"><code>port</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/protocol\"><code>protocol</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/search\"><code>search</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/searchParams\"><code>searchParams</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/username\"><code>username</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURl\"><code>createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>revokeObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/toJSON\"><code>toJSON()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/toString\"><code>toString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a URL API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"> <div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta é uma <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tecnologia experimental (en-US)</a></strong><br>Verifique a <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">tabela de compatibilidade entre Navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usar essa funcionalidade em produção.</p></div></div>\n\n<p>The <strong><code>URL</code></strong><strong> </strong>interface represent an object providing static methods used for creating object URLs.</p>\n\n<p>When using a user agent where no constructor has been implemented yet, it is possible to access such an object using the non-standard <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>Window.URL</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> properties (prefixed with Webkit- and Blink-based browser as <code>Window.webkitURL</code>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Implements properties defined in <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils</code></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.href\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.href</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing the whole URL.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.protocol\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.protocol</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing the protocol scheme of the URL, including the final <code>':'</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.host\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.host</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing the host, that is the <em>hostname</em>, a <code>':'</code>, and the <em>port</em> of the URL.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.hostname\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.hostname</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing the domain of the URL.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.port\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.port</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing the port number of the URL.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.pathname\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.pathname</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing an initial <code>'/'</code> followed by the path of the URL.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.search\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.search</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing a <code>'?'</code> followed by the parameters of the URL.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.hash\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.hash</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing a <code>'#'</code> followed by the fragment identifier of the URL.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.username\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.username</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing the username specified before the domain name.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.password\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.password</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Is a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing the password specified before the domain name.</dd>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.origin\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.origin</code></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing the origin of the URL, that is its scheme, its domain and its port.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.searchparams\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.searchParams</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URLSearchParams\"><code>URLSearchParams</code></a> object allowing to access the GET query arguments contained in the URL.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructor","title":"Constructor","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"url_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/URL\"><code>URL()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Creates and return a <code>URL</code> object composed from the given parameters.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>The <code>URL</code> interface implements methods defined in <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils</code></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"urlutils.tostring\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.toString()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing the whole URL. It is a synonym for <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>URLUtils.href</code></a>, though it can't be used to modify the value.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"static_methods","title":"Static methods","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"url.createobjecturl\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURl\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> containing a unique blob URL, that is a URL with <code>blob:</code> as its scheme, followed by an opaque string uniquely identifying the object in the browser.</dd>\n <dt id=\"url.revokeobjecturl\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>URL.revokeObjectURL()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Revokes an object URL previously created using <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURl\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/FileAPI/#creating-revoking\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">File API<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'URL' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Rascunho atual</span></td>\n   <td>Added the static methods <code>URL.createObjectURL()</code> and <code>URL.revokeObjectURL</code><code>()</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://url.spec.whatwg.org/#api\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">URL<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Node' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition (implements <code>URLUtils</code>).</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.URL","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>[1] From Gecko 2 (Firefox 4) to Gecko 18 included, Gecko supported this interface with the non-standard <code>nsIDOMMozURLProperty</code> internal type. As the only to access such an object was through <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>window.URL</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, in practice, this didn't make any difference.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"chrome_code_-_scope_availability","title":"Chrome Code - Scope Availability","isH3":false,"content":"<p>To use from chrome code, JSM and Bootstrap scope, you have to import it like this:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>Cu<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">importGlobalProperties</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'URL'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><code>URL</code> is available in Worker scopes.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Property allowing to get such an object: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL\"><code>Window.URL</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Components.utils.importGlobalProperties\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Components.utils.importGlobalProperties</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Constructor","id":"constructor"},{"text":"Methods","id":"methods"},{"text":"Static methods","id":"static_methods"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Chrome Code - Scope Availability","id":"chrome_code_-_scope_availability"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The URL interface represent an object providing static methods used for creating object URLs.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"URL","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"URL","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"URL","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"URL","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"URL","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"URL","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"URL","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"URL","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"URL","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/url","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/url/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/URL","title":"URL"}],"pageTitle":"URL - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}